+------+-----+                     +------+---------------------+
       |                                  |
       |                                  |
+------v-----+                     +------v----------------------+
|SUMMON_BULB |                     |CALCULATE_ENEMY_POSSIBILITIES|
+------+-----+                     +------+----------------------+
       |                                  |
